description: Want to learn amazing potato facts from your friend the potato dude?  Of course you do.  New facts added often to give you facts about this often misunderstood vegetable.  Did you know there is more vitamin C in a potato than an orange?  To learn more about the potato, just ask Alexa about the potato dude!
